# EXYONE@BLOG:~$

> A technical blog about .NET, front-end development, and web technologies. Built with Eleventy (11ty), featuring a three-column glassmorphism layout, PWA support, client-side search, and Giscus comments.

Author: Exyone.dev — software developer based in China, turning curiosity into code.

## Posts

- [用Eleventy搭建静态博客的完整指南](/posts/eleventy-guide/): A complete guide to building a modern blog with Eleventy, covering project structure, templates, data files, and deployment.
- [CSS自定义属性实现主题切换](/posts/css-custom-properties/): Using CSS Custom Properties for flexible theme configuration including color schemes, typography, and layout parameters.
- [响应式设计的最佳实践](/posts/responsive-design/): Modern responsive design strategies including mobile-first approach, flexible layouts, and breakpoint selection.
- [读书笔记：代码整洁之道](/posts/clean-code-notes/): Reading notes on "Clean Code" summarizing core principles about naming, functions, and comments.
- [记一次周末徒步](/posts/weekend-hiking/): A personal travelogue about a spring weekend hiking trip in the suburbs.
- [Docker容器化部署实践](/posts/docker-deployment/): Practical experience with Docker containerization, multi-stage builds, and Docker Compose orchestration.

